AB  - This paper mainly discussed the security of dangerous containers can be improved at the seaport containers yard during the dangerous containers allocation the berth and seaport containers yard by concerning the personal risk and the social risk. The security of dangerous containers have been substantially higher than other sectors in the security perspective, especially for the dangerous goods. There is a large number of technologies available for assessing the security of dangerous containers during the loading the containers yard, which can be classified according to the weighted security risk value chains used by the weighted complex networks technology. risk weighted equipment, which is quantizated risk dangerous goods containers, such as the radio frequency identification technologies, allows real-time weighted risk visibility of the containers and managers. A novel research model for the weighted risk optimization of the dangerous-goods container yard was developed based on the dangerous goods container yard security technology acceptance the storage model. Furthermore, the results suggest that security perspective strongly effects on the perceived ease of using the dangerous-goods container yard. This implies that system operators should further enhance data security to increase the intention to adopt the monitoring equipment.
